Third-party attribution
=======================

GL-INET-BERYL-AX-HOLSTER
------------------------

This repository imports and modifies an exported STL of:

- "GL-INET-BERYL-AX-HOLSTER" by DunknDonuts
- MakerWorld: https://makerworld.com/en/models/428474-gl-inet-beryl-ax-holster
- Source CAD: https://cad.onshape.com/documents/4fd11188d706b52e56b15526/w/7970faa89563f7f57c9aa723/e/5b438853887219bc6ade6645
- Local reference file: reference/GL-INET-BERYL-AX-HOLSTER.stl

The active OpenSCAD model imports the STL, scales it to millimeters, subtracts
and unions additional geometry, and adds HomeRacker-compatible sleeve features.
It does not edit the upstream Onshape CAD document.
